{
  "texts": [
    "The final response of the fine-tuned model is expected to be consistent with its reasoning, i.e.",
    "P θ (r (F) rej |r (R) rej) ≈ P θ (r (F) comp |r (R) comp) ≈ 1, thereby reinforcing robust and context-aware decision-making.",
    "This follows our assumption P (r (F) rej |r (R) rej) = P (r (F) comp |r (R) comp) = 1 in the curated Rationale dataset.",
    "This implies that once the model establishes a reasoning-based decision, the corresponding rejection or compliance response follows deterministically.",
    "Thus, the fine-tuning process primarily focuses on aligning the reasoning capabilities, ensuring accurate discernment of the intent and ethical implications of a given prompt."
  ]
